2.1.2.1.4 Customer JSON Schema
{
    "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#",
    "type": "object",
    "title": "Customer",
    "properties": {
        "customer_id": {
            "type": "integer"
        },
        "name": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "customer_group_id": {
            "type": "integer"
        },
        "email": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "email"
        },
        "phone_number": {
            "type": "string"
        }
    },
    "additionalProperties": false,
    "required": [
        "customer_id",
        "name"
    ]
}
